### Frontend — Service Layer

#### [NEW] [skinCareService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/skinCareService.js)

Thin axios wrapper (same pattern as [dietService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/dietService.js)):
- `getPlan()` — GET `/skincare/plan`
- `generatePlan(products)` — POST `/skincare/plan`
- `logTask(date, data)` — POST `/skincare/log`
- `getLog(date)` — GET `/skincare/log/:date`
- `getCalendar()` — GET `/skincare/calendar`

---

### Frontend — Page Component

#### [MODIFY] [SkinCare.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/components/pages/SkinCare.jsx)

Replace the stub with a full page. The page has **3 states**:

**State 1 — Onboarding (no plan exists)**
- Show product selection UI with categories:
  - **Allopathic**: Cleanser, Moisturizer, Sunscreen, Serum, Retinoid, etc.
  - **Homeopathic**: Aloe Vera Gel, Rose Water, Neem Face Wash, Turmeric Cream, etc.
- Multi-select from predefined options + "Add Custom" input
- "Generate My Plan" button → calls API → AI generates routine

**State 2 — Daily Routine View (plan exists)**
- Morning & Night routine cards with checkboxes per step
- "Follow for X days/months" badge at top
- Tips section from AI
- "Update Products" button → goes back to State 1

**State 3 — Calendar / History View**
- Monthly calendar grid (current month)
- Each day cell shows: ✅ (all done), 🟡 (partial), ❌ (nothing), or empty (no data)
- Click a day → see that day's log, can toggle tasks retroactively
- Navigate between months (within data range)

All styled with **Tailwind CSS 4 + dark mode** matching the existing Slate/Emerald/Pink palette used in [Activity.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/components/pages/Activity.jsx) and [Diet.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/components/pages/Diet.jsx).

